headline: Oil Holds Decline as Traders Assess Outlook for Russian Supply
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Oil held a drop — after slumping by 1.6% on Monday — as US President Donald Trump’s latest plan to pressure Russia refrained from immediate new measures aimed at hindering Moscow’s energy exports.
